## Audio Processing
- Sample rate: 16,000 Hz
- Format: FLAC (output.flac)
- Minimum recording length: 1 second
- Short recordings (<0.5s) force clipboard usage

## Key Bindings
- Right CTRL: Record toggle
- Right SHIFT: Enable Dutch translation
- ENTER or '/': Get ChatGPT response

## Environment Setup
Uses virtual environment ([venv/](mdc:venv/)) for dependency isolation. Always activate before running or building.
